00:20:46.900 --> 00:20:50.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
ジャガイモ料理に
類さん 感動！

377
00:20:50.266 --> 00:20:51.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
（吉田）ジャガイモを
