00:21:08.033 --> 00:21:09.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
いただきます

384
00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:13.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
