387
00:21:16.966 --> 00:21:18.000  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
キタアカリで

388
00:21:18.100 --> 00:21:19.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
（高橋）
キタアカリのほうを

