00:23:06.466 --> 00:23:09.666  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
キュンと
胸に来るというような

421
00:23:09.766 --> 00:23:10.533  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
