00:23:22.666 --> 00:23:24.266  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
（吉田）
土のよさだと思いますね

427
00:23:24.366 --> 00:23:25.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
こういうとこ
地球上に―

428
00:23:25.900 --> 00:23:27.500  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
