今回の旅

432
00:23:36.966 --> 00:23:38.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
おいしい料理と―

433
00:23:38.866 --> 00:23:41.800  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
おいしいお酒を
堪能しました

434
00:23:42.766 --> 00:23:43.900  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:10.00% 
さあ 類さん

435
